  "texts": [
    "Zhang et al. [218] proposed a DL-based channel estimation algorithm for the OTFS-based ISAC in vehicular systems.",
    "In particular, they transformed the channel estimation task into a 2-dimensional sparse signal denoising problem, and used a deep convolutional residual network with an adaptive threshold to estimate the CSI, which showed better estimation performance than the traditional algorithms.",
    "Hu et al. [219] designed a transformer-based ISAC receiver, which can perform the communication symbol detection and sensor parameter estimation simultaneously, demonstrating more robust performance than the RNN-based baseline.",
    "Different from the above point-target model, Dehkordi et al. [220] investigated the extended target parameter estimation for ISAC systems.",
    "They developed a DNN based on VAE and a regression network to estimate the spatial extent of the extended target instead of all the scattering points."
